{"tid":1754931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"區選打飛機到今晚12點就停啦好嗎","createTime":"2019-11-25T11:25:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T15:44:58.000Z","uid":148406,"like":83,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"ed29833f55ebafb6bb21d09f0dcafc3f0b4f4641","tid":1754931,"uid":148406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:25:38.000Z","msg":"望下個熱門<br />\n行動po呢?<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，未有<br />\n理大手足，未走<br />\n前線手足，未抖<br />\n被咬手足，未安全<br />\n<br />\n打贏一場<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">戰鬥</span></strong>係要慶祝<br />\n振奮下士氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係對家同時已經係到諗緊下幾步棋<br />\n要點對付我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記著，<br />\n而家打緊既係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">戰爭</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一子錯，滿盤皆落索<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n差不多係時侯啦手足<br />\n我地繼續一齊行落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求　缺一不可<br />\n光復香港　時代革命<br />\n香港人　報仇<br />\n<br />\n幫我推上熱門，好嗎?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c6b43f7bc5be22c8f7a731b4baeac555f1a1aaa","tid":1754931,"uid":191309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:26:50.000Z","msg":"好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b26c3810801748f99ba5df0659299e824efe3ef","tid":1754931,"uid":43178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:27:06.000Z","msg":"好"},{"pid":"2b512db322ae28781eed655ddae752b697bcaf8f","tid":1754931,"uid":63639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:27:54.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"facbdc165bb65f2075315be3f4b0d6f0d6266f3d","tid":1754931,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT